The paper deals with remote sensing image change detection using deep learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and generative adversarial networks (GANs) also suggests that the paper may belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves image processing and analysis, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
